{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, we will first analyse whether the data with which the GenAI technology is 'fed' (the input) can raise questions regarding legality, and then, we will investigate whether the results obtained by processing the data (the output) can involve legal aspects, particularly civil liability.",
    "We will not address the process phase, as it comprises no legal aspects, but only technical ones.",
    "In the first part we will clarify the distinct types of data that can be used as training data for GenAI.",
    "Following that, we will discuss some recent litigation involving training data that is alleged to infringe intellectual property rights.",
    "Where does the data that feeds and trains a GenAI technology come from?"
  ]
}